Yordanov Voted Bulgaria 's Best 1998 Soccer Player
SOFIA , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- International midfielder Ivailo Yordanov from Sporting Lisbon was voted Bulgaria 's Footballer of the Year on Monday .
The 30-year-old player has played 42 matches and scored three goals for the Bulgarian national team .
Yordanov fought his way back into the Bulgarian team and played at the World Cup finals in France after being diagnosed as suffering from multiple sclerosis last year .
